/BEGIN home.html.haml

- if signed_in?
  %table.front{:summary => "For signed-in users"}
    %tr
      %td.main
        %h1.micropost What's up?
        = render 'shared/micropost_form'
        = render 'shared/feed'

      %td.sidebar.round
        = render 'shared/user_info'
        = render 'shared/stats'
        = image_tag('feed.png')
        = link_to "Subscribe", private_user_feed_path(@user.username,
                               @user.encrypted_password, :format => :rss)
     
- else
  = link_to "Sign up now!", signup_path, :class => "signup_button round"

  %h1
    %i Welcome!

  %p
    Hi and welcome to The Microblog Project. This is basically a website
    which is based on the concept of twiiter

  %h1
    %i What's been added?



  %p
    Here's what's been added so far. I'm currently working on the last two extensions.

  %table
    %tr
      %td 1. Replies
      %td 3. Follower notifications
      %td 5. Signup confirmation

    %tr
      %td 2. Messaging
      %td 4. Password reminders
      %td 6. RSS feed




/END pages/home.html.haml
